# Working data — bank exports, the master ledger, normalized/triage state, routed
# batches. Everything under data/ is private financial state and must never be
# committed.
data/*
!data/.gitkeep

# Account map (may reveal which banks/accounts you hold) — copy
# accounts.example.json to accounts.json and fill it in. Never commit the real one.
accounts.json

# Any generated reports routed out to the forms.
*.xlsx
